
Each element and attribute has one parent!
book is parent of title, author, year and price

Elements may have zero, one or more children!
title, author, year and price elements are children of book

Siblings: nodes having the same parent
title author, year and price are siblings

<book>
  <title>Harry Potter</title>
  <author>J K. Rowling</author>
  <year>2005</year>
  <price>29.99</price>
</book> 


Ancestors: A node's parent, parent's parent ..
ancestors of title are book and bookstore

Descendants: node's chidren, children's children ..
book, title, author, year, price are descendants of bookstore

<bookstore>

<book>
  <title>Harry Potter</title>
  <author>J K. Rowling</author>
  <year>2005</year>
  <price>29.99</price>
</book>

</bookstore> 
